description:
The egg that started Eggstyle.
A 1996 Toyota Previa DX — base model, rear‑wheel drive, supercharged. This was my very first egg, the one that pulled me into the world of Previas and never let go. I learned so much about the chassis from this van; every bolt, rattle, and quirk taught me something new. The obsession only grew from here, but it all started with this one.
